---
title: Cheese & Chorizo Loaded Chilli Beef Enchiladas with Fresh Guacamole, Crispy Wedges and Limey Sour Cream
description: We love good Beef Enchiladas with Chorizo & Wedges and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chilli-cheese-beef-enchiladas-76f6ec94-fba97252.jpg
